pwd (path working directory): lenh in duong dan den vi tri ban dang xem.

cd (Change Directory): dung de di chuye
  + cd ..: chuyen len thu muc 1 cap.
  + cd: ve thang thu muc home.
  + cd-: di chuyen den thu muc o truoc do.

ls (list): hien thi danh sach tap tin va thu muc co trong thu muc dang xem:
  + ls -R: liet ke cac fiel bao gom ca cac thu muc o ben trong.
  + ls -l: liet ke cac quyen cua cac file va folder.
  + ls -a : liet ke tat ca, ke ca cac file an.

cat (concatenate): de xem noi dung tren file:
  + cat > namefile: tao ra new file.
  + cat namefile1 namefile2 > namefile3: nhap file 1, 2 -> 3.
  + cat namefile | tr a-z A-Z > output.txt: chuyen tu in tuong sang in hoa va nguoc lai.

cp (copy) dung de sao chep:
  + cp file /xx/xxx/xxx.

mv (move) di chuyen hoac doi ten:
  + mv oldfile.txt newfile.txt
  + mv file.txt /home/user/documents/

mkdir (make directory) tao thu muc
  + mkdir namedirectiry.

rm (remove) xoa cac file or folder.
  
touch de tao file: 
  + /home/username/Documents/Web.html


grep "string can search" name_file (search strong in file).
sort <option> <file>: sort tang hoac giam.
rmdir name_folder: detele folder.
